
Pindel

_run_Pindel --> pindel_all.pbs

	pindel_setup.sh
		= ${PATIENT}.pindel.cfg	

	${PINDEL} (module pindel)
		= ${PATIENT}.pindel

	${PINDEL2VCF} (module pindel2vcf)
		= ${PATIENT}.pindel.vcf

	${PYTHON_VCF2TDT} (= vcf2tdt.py)
		= ${PATIENT}.pindel.vcf.tdt == ${PATIENT}.indels

	${SH_PINDEL_FILTER} (= pindel_filter.sh)
		${PYTHON_PINDEL_FILTER} (= pindel_filter.py)
			= ${datafile}.filter

		${BEDTOOLS} (module bedtools)
			= ${datafile}.filter.intersect

	${SH_PINDEL_ANNOTATE} (= pindel_annotate.sh)
		annotate_variation.pl 

		annotation_COSMIC.py
		annotation_KINASE.py
		annotation_CANCER.py
			

==============================================

Simple large deletions
medium size insertions

user defined Maximum Deletion Size

*D   = Large Deletions
*SI  = Short insertions
LI  = Long insertions
*INV = Inversions
TD  = Tandem duplications
BP  = breakpoints
*RP  = split-read evidence of larger variants

